        {
          "component_id": "artifact_list",
          "data": {
            "circlet_of_logos": {
              "desc": "便宜的饰物，却是远古时代的陨星带来的奇特的金属制成。",
              "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Tiny Miracle/circlet_of_logos_icon.png",
              "position": "理之冠",
              "title": "奇迹耳坠"
            },
            "flower_of_life": {
              "desc": "岩石之中生长出来的花。能够裂穿坚硬的岩壁，是因为花追寻着光。",
              "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Tiny Miracle/flower_of_life_icon.png",
              "position": "生之花",
              "title": "奇迹之花"
            },
            "goblet_of_eonothem": {
              "desc": "民间流传的算命仪式使用的杯子，也可以装水。",
              "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Tiny Miracle/goblet_of_eonothem_icon.png",
              "position": "空之杯",
              "title": "奇迹之杯"
            },
            "plume_of_death": {
              "desc": "来自速度极快的猛禽，那奇迹般的一击肉眼几乎无法捕捉。",
              "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Tiny Miracle/plume_of_death_icon.png",
              "position": "死之羽",
              "title": "奇迹之羽"
            },
            "sands_of_eon": {
              "desc": "看上去是寻常的沙漏，干涸的沙砾随着翻转运动像水一样流动。",
              "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Tiny Miracle/sands_of_eon_icon.png",
              "position": "时之沙",
              "title": "奇迹之沙"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "16",
      "name": "故事",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "story",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "desc": "</br>小小的蓝色鲜花，从古老的残损石碑中生长出来。</br>残碑承载着死的历史，裂缝中却孕育着生的奇迹。</br></br>",
                "img": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Tiny Miracle/flower_of_life_icon.png",
                "title": "奇迹之花"
              },
              {
                "desc": "</br>一对不算昂贵的耳坠，以星光般闪亮的金属雕琢而成。</br>商贩所不知的是，它的闪耀来自远古坠落大地的星星。</br></br>",
                "img": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Tiny Miracle/circlet_of_logos_icon.png",
                "title": "奇迹耳坠"
              },
              {
                "desc": "</br>清白的茶盏，其中闪烁着星光。</br>过去曾有占卜者用它卜问吉凶，</br>是相信水中能映出星辰的海洋。</br></br>",
                "img": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Tiny Miracle/goblet_of_eonothem_icon.png",
                "title": "奇迹之杯"
              },
              {
                "desc": "</br>与风同速的猛禽，其存在本身便是奇迹。</br>它被赐予了锐利的视觉和锋刃般的脚爪，</br>又有宽广的翼展，得以支撑它高速滑翔。</br></br>",
                "img": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Tiny Miracle/plume_of_death_icon.png",
                "title": "奇迹之羽"
              },
              {
                "desc": "</br>常说胜利需要争取，但奇迹却只能等待。</br>但是磐石被磨成细沙，难道不是奇迹吗？</br>你与我的相遇，难道不也是一种奇迹吗？</br></br>",
                "img": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Tiny Miracle/sands_of_eon_icon.png",
                "title": "奇迹之沙"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
